	\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"t.cn 短域名 WordPress 插件\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:113:\"http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 25 Jan 2011 17:41:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress 插件\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"新浪微博\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"http://fairyfish.net/?p=3042\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:118:\"t.cn 短域名 WordPress 插件，能够获取每篇日志的 t.cn 短域名，并且显示在日志的内容后面。\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Denis\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4398:\"<p>大家都知道新浪有个 t.cn 的短网址，如果给每篇日志生成一个这样的短链接绝对拉风，分享的时候也非常方便。今天我就做个 WordPress 插件，能够获取每篇日志的 t.cn 短网址，并且显示在日志的内容后面。</p>\n<p>使用非常简单，只需要上传激活即可。比如这篇日志的 url 是：<a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed&amp;utm_content=content\">http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/</a>，它的 t.cn 短网址就是：<a href=\"http://t.cn/hGe7Dg?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed&amp;utm_content=content\">http://t.cn/hGe7Dg</a></p>\n<p>如果想定义日志后面显示的效果，你可以通过 <code>t_cn_link</code> 这个 class 来定义 CSS。</p>\n<p>如果其他插件想调用当前日志的 t.cn 的短网址，可以使用如下代码：</p>\n<pre>$t_cn = get_post_t_cn($post_ID);</pre>\n<p>如果要获取某个 url 的短网址，可以使用如下的代码：</p>\n<pre>$t_cn = get_t_cn($long_url);</pre>\n<p>以后还将增加统计和评论数功能，和新浪微博完全整合 <img src=\'http://fairyfish.net/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\' alt=\':-)\' class=\'wp-smiley\' />  。</p>\n<p>感谢 <a href=\"http://lightcss.com/?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed&amp;utm_content=content\">Sivan</a> 帮我测试。</p>\n<p>下载：<a href=\"http://wpcn.googlecode.com/files/t-cn-wordpress.php?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed&amp;utm_content=content\">t.cn 短网址 WordPress 插件</a></p>\n<p>&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed&amp;utm_content=content_more\" title=\"t.cn 短域名 WordPress 插件\">继续阅读全文</a> ...</p><hr /><p><a href=\"http://ipaddh.com/?utm_source=fairyfishfeed&utm_medium=cpm&utm_content=banner&utm_campaign=fairyfishfeed\"><img src=\"http://ipaddh.com/wp-content/themes/ipaddh/ipadDHrssbanner.jpg\"></a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n&copy; <a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/\" title=\"我爱水煮鱼\">我爱水煮鱼</a>\r\n / <a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/bookmark/?url=http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/&title=t.cn+%E7%9F%AD%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D+WordPress+%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6&tags=WordPress 插件, 新浪微博, \"  title=\"t.cn 短域名 WordPress 插件\">收藏本文</a>\r\n / <a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2011/01/26/t-cn-wordpress-plugin/#comments\" title=\"t.cn 短域名 WordPress 插件\">24条评论</a>\r\n / <a href=\"http://feed.fairyfish.net\" title=\"订阅我爱水煮鱼\">RSS 订阅</a>\r\n / <a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/go/wpjam\" title=\"WordPress JAM\">长期承接 WordPress 项目</a>\r\n / <a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/coupon/\" title=\"主机域名优惠码\">主机域名优惠码</a>\r\n / <a href=\"http://t.sina.com.cn/denishua/\" title=\"新浪微博\">新浪微博</a>\r\n</p><h3>相关日志</h3><ul class=\"related_post\"><li><a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/m/sina-connect-20/\" title=\"新浪微博连接 2.0\">新浪微博连接 2.0</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2010/06/17/wp-sina-t/\" title=\"同步 WordPress 博客日志到新浪微博\">同步 WordPress 博客日志到新浪微博</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2010/06/08/sina-connect/\" title=\"新浪微博连接：使用新浪微博登陆 WordPress 博客\">新浪微博连接：使用新浪微博登陆 WordPress 博客</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2009/06/16/single-sign-on/\" title=\"单点登录介绍和在 WordPress 中的应用\">单点登录介绍和在 WordPress 中的应用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/m/unified-connect-button-style/\" title=\"统一新浪微博连接，腾讯微博连接，豆瓣连接的图标风格\">统一新浪微博连接，腾讯微博连接，豆瓣连接的图标风格</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://fairyfish.net/2010/12/23/wpjam-vshop/\" title=\"基于 WordPress 虚拟商品销售的商城系统\">基于 WordPress 虚拟商品销售的商城系统</a></li>\n</ul><img src=\"http://fairyfish.net/wp-content/plugins/all-in-one/ga.php?utmac=MO-328125-5&amp;utmn=59836884&amp;utmr=-&amp;utmp=%2Frss%2F2011%2F01%2F26%2Ft-cn-wordpress-plugin%2F&amp;utmdt=t.cn+%E7%9F%AD%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D+WordPress+%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6&amp;guid=ON\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a